<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Order Completed - Success!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background: #28a745;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .details {
            background: white;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            background: #28a745;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .success-badge {
            background: #d4edda;
            color: #155724;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>âœ… Order Completed Successfully!</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello <%= Recipient %>,</h2>

            <div class="success-badge">
                <strong>ðŸŽ‰ Your order has been completed successfully!</strong>
            </div>

            <p>We're pleased to inform you that your truck order has been <strong>COMPLETED</strong>.</p>

            <div class="details">
                <h3>ðŸ“‹ Completed Order Details:</h3>
                <p><strong>Truck ID:</strong>
                    <%= TruckId %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>Loading Depot:</strong>
                    <%= LoadingDepot %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>Destination:</strong>
                    <%= Destination %>, <%= City %>, <%= State %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>Completion Time:</strong>
                    <%= OrderTime %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>Completed By:</strong>
                    <%= Sender %>
                </p>
            </div>

            <p>Thank you for choosing FuelsGate for your transportation needs. We hope you had a great experience with
                our service.</p>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= OrderUrl %>" class="button">View Order Summary</a>
            </div>

            <p><strong>What's Next?</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>You can view your completed order details in your dashboard</li>
                <li>Rate your experience with this truck owner/transporter</li>
                <li>Download your ticket</li>
                <li>Book your next order with us!</li>
            </ul>

            <p>Thank you for your business!</p>
            
        </div>

        <%- include("./shared/footer") %>

    </div>
</body>

</html>